&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Seasonal Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop differentiated product promotion strategies along with season change, such as for key Western shopping events (e.g., Black Friday, Prime Day, Back to School).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Eyewear Logic Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Optimize the visibility and flow of the shopping experience. Improve the UI/UX of the Prescription (Rx) and LC upload process to minimize friction and bounce rates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Categorization:&lt;/strong&gt; Execute scientific sorting and filtering based on Face Shape, Materials (Acetate, Titanium), and Lens Functions (Blue Light Blocking, Photochromic).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
